	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />does anyone know how to add an english patch to a japanese rom?  i know you can patch it through the emulator, but i wanted to know how to incorporate it into the rom.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
