	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I recommend you not to patch your original roms, instead use nestopia's patch on the fly. All you need it the ips filename to match the rom filename, and put it in ips folder. This way you can both keep your japanese roms clean and enjoy the translation

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

