	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I personally like to make a copy of the original ROM and to apply the patch to the duplicate.  This way, I can have both the original and the patch and can select between them easily in the Open dialog.
<br />
<br />That's my taste, though, and I fully respect those who prefer soft patching.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
